data.description: Sitting on over an acre, this Harlem home holds the charm and space you're looking for. This ranch home, built in 2018 offers 9' ceilings, Evacore flooring in main living area, thermostat radiant barrier roofing and so much more. The thoughtfully designed floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family.  Vaulted ceiling great room with wood-burning fireplace for cozy winter evenings. The kitchen has spacious island, coffered ceiling, subway tile backsplash and dine in area. Owner's suite includes a sitting area and ensuite with tiled shower and separate tub. 3 additional bedrooms and a full bath. Enjoy your 1.15 acre lot with a covered back porch and wooded view. EV Outlet and 30 amp in the garage!
